      <title>《独立报》控制了 BuzzFeed UK 和 HuffPost UK</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-28/the-independent-takes-control-of-buzzfeed-uk-and-huffpost-uk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[BuzzFeed Inc. 曾经是颠覆性在线媒体的典型代表，该公司将把其英国和爱尔兰业务的剩余部分交给英国新闻公司独立数字新闻与媒体。 Media Ltd. 签订长期许可协议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-28/the-independent-takes-control-of-buzzfeed-uk-and-huffpost-uk</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 14:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Altice 如何推动债权人削减数十亿美元的债务：问答</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-28/altice-q-a-how-drahi-can-push-creditors-to-cut-billions-of-debt</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亿万富翁帕特里克·德拉希 (Patrick Drahi) 的 Altice 正在要求债权人同意承担损失，因为该公司陷入困境的法国电信部门正在努力削减近 250 亿欧元（合 270 亿美元）的债务负担。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-28/altice-q-a-how-drahi-can-push-creditors-to-cut-billions-of-debt</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 13:27:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
